    {"id":"an-t","type":"text","x":400,"y":115,"width":230,"height":150,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"seed":4,"version":1,"versionNonce":4,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":14,"fontFamily":1,"text":"Anthropic\n自上而下 · 竞技期最优\n\n• 价值观面试统一方向\n• Dario 两周一次全员 memo\n• 管杀也管埋——迭代极快\n• 适合聚焦攻坚\n\nClaude Code 几十天迭代\n几十个功能，每周都在升级","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Anthropic\n自上而下 · 竞技期最优\n\n• 价值观面试统一方向\n• Dario 两周一次全员 memo\n• 管杀也管埋——迭代极快\n• 适合聚焦攻坚\n\nClaude Code 几十天迭代\n几十个功能，每周都在升级","lineHeight":1.3,"baseline":166},

    {"id":"note-bot","type":"text","x":60,"y":320,"width":580,"height":90,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#862e9c","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"seed":5,"version":1,"versionNonce":5,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":14,"fontFamily":1,"text":"关键洞察：两种组织形态适合不同阶段\n• 探索期（AI 不知道能做什么）→ 自下而上、发散\n• 赛跑期（主线收敛到 coding）→ 自上而下、对齐\n• 如果下一个范式诞生，可能又重新需要发散型组织","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"middle","containerId":null,"originalText":"关键洞察：两种组织形态适合不同阶段\n• 探索期（AI 不知道能做什么）→ 自下而上、发散\n• 赛跑期（主线收敛到 coding）→ 自上而下、对齐\n• 如果下一个范式诞生，可能又重新需要发散型组织","lineHeight":1.5,"baseline":74},

